      "description": "Experimental hemolysis index measurements collected at five adult operating points (2.5, 3.5, 4.0, 5.0, 6.0 L/min at 2400–3600 RPM) using porcine blood in a closed-loop circuit. CFD-predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) agreed with measurements within 12% across all points. Dataset collected and analysis completed November 2021, prior to the Q1 2024 paediatric indication expansion.",
      "generatedAtTime": "2021-11-30T00:00:00Z"
